## Verification

| Feature | Test |
|---|---|
| Toast position | Any action → toast appears bottom-left |
| Revert confirm | Complete a habit, click again → confirm dialog |
| Header dropdown | Click username → dropdown with Settings + Logout |
| Daily view | Only shows habits scheduled for today |
| Calendar view | Pick past date → habits for that date; toggle creates log |
| All view | All habits visible |
| HabitLog | `POST /api/habits/1/log` → row in `habit_logs` table |
| Streak | Complete 2 days in a row → fiery cube, streak badge |
| Freeze earned | 7-day streak → `streak_freezes.count` increments |
| Freeze consumed | Miss a scheduled day → nightly job creates frozen log, count decrements |
| Icon picker | Search + select → habit card shows icon |
| Recurrence end | Set end date → habit disappears from daily view after that date |
| Reminder push | Set reminder 1 min ahead → push notification fires |
| Change password | New password works after update |
| Export | JSON file downloaded with habits + logs |
| Delete account | Account gone, session cleared, redirected to `/` |
